## Phase 5: Decision Matrix

### The Replay Score Card

Run this for each earnings target. Score each factor and sum:

| Factor | Bullish (+) | Neutral (0) | Bearish (-) |
|--------|-------------|-------------|-------------|
| **DP 5d Trend** | Accumulating (+2) | Flat (0) | Distributing (-2) |
| **Short Vol %** | < 45% (+1) | 45-55% (0) | > 55% (-1) |
| **DP Position Sign** | Positive (+1) | Near-zero (0) | Negative (-1) |
| **52w Range Position** | 20-60% (+1) | 60-80% (0) | <20% or >80% (-1) |
| **VIX Regime** | Level 1-2 (+1) | Level 3 (0) | Level 4 (-1) |
| **Signal List** | On bullish list (+1) | Not listed (0) | On bearish list (-1) |
| **SPY Gamma** | Above call wall (+1) | Between walls (0) | Below put wall (-1) |
| **Sector Momentum** | Peers rallying (+1) | Mixed (0) | Peers selling (-1) |

### Score Interpretation

| Score | Action | Sizing |
|-------|--------|--------|
| +5 to +8 | 🟢 LEAN LONG | Full size (1-2% of portfolio) |
| +2 to +4 | 🟡 LEAN LONG (cautious) | Half size |
| -1 to +1 | ⚪ NEUTRAL | No position or small straddle |
| -4 to -2 | 🟡 LEAN SHORT (cautious) | Half size puts |
| -8 to -5 | 🔴 LEAN SHORT | Full size puts |

